      "title": "Research regarding debriefing as part of the learning process",
      "abstract": "Introduction:Debriefing is a process involving the active participation of learners, guided by a facilitator or instructor whose primary goal is to identify and close gaps in knowledge and skills. A review of existing research and a process for identifying future opportunities was undertaken.Methods"
